attributes.Long form description: The student first exchanges the GoPro battery for a new one. Then, the student exchanges the SD card for a new one. Afterward, the student turns on the GoPro, in the process, the student incorrectly turns on the GoPro with the recording button and is corrected by the instructor. Later, the student turns off the GoPro. Then, the student attaches the GoPro to a strap, with difficulty. The student then exchanges the strap for the handheld grip. Next, the student exchanges the handheld grip for the tripod. Lastly, the student removes the GoPro from the tripod.
